name: China Eastern 777-39PER [B-2022] Takeoff and Landing at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Another old clip from Paine Field! Here we have a China Eastern 777-300ER taxiing, taking off, and landing back at Paine Field, Boeing's plant in Everett, Washington. Listen to those GE90s on the takeoff! Enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
